data.title: State Records : Baseball
data.text:
Cameron Varga, Cincinnati Hills Christian Academy - 2014, over four games:

5/2 vs. Summit Country Day, last out of game

5/8 vs. Clark Montessori, 15 strikeouts in 5 inning perfect game

5/16 vs. East Clinton in Sectional Tournament, no-hitter, one batter reached on a passed ball after a strikeout
